      • UNAVAILABLE_INFORMATION

        public static final long UNAVAILABLE_INFORMATION
        This should be ~0L, but the adapter is 32bit, so it can only ever be 0xFFFFFFFF. To avoid a problem with values not matching, we will get this constant by querying the underlying Cryptoki provider.
